title: Moore throws for 2 TDs, Cincinnati beats Miami 34-23
text:
> Florida Moore throws for 2 TDs, Cincinnati beats Miami 34-23 University of Cincinnati President Santa Ono plays cello with an ensemble from the Cincinnati Young Artists as they play the National Anthem before an NCAA college football game against Miami, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015, in Cincinnati. (AP Photo/Gary Landers)
